workout_items.name: EMOM (every min on the min) 20mins
workout_items.info:
1 min - 8 burpees
1 min - 40 crisscross
1 min - 20 crunches
1 min - 15 bicep curls (use heavy items)

Do the exercise on the strike of the minute. If it takes your 40s to do 8 burpees, you have 20s rest. If it takes you 50s, you have 10s rest. Next min do the next exercise.
